main event: A civilian witness reported sighting a white, dull glowing object that flashed slowly on and off at a high altitude in Colorado on January 25, 1967.
interesting points: The object was described as round in shape and the size of a dime.
The object was observed to descend slightly to the left during its flight.
The sighting lasted for approximately 5 minutes.
No sound was reported from the object.
The sighting occurred near Stapleton Airport.
